{
  "stem": "21919.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, well, whichever's gonna call us first, that's where we going to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it happened that the Canadian consul called us for Thursday, and the American for Friday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So since I had said that already, he stuck to that idea, and we went to the Canadian consul.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And because I was pregnant with my second child, they made sure that I got out before seven months pregnancy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came by boat to Halifax.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was called It was sort of like a military boat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from Halifax, we traveled by train to Winnipeg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came in 1950, in May.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Winnipeg had a big flood that year, and we arrived in a very-- [SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very bad time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came to-- to a second cousin of mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stayed for a few days with them, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] maybe even a couple of weeks, then we started looking for a place to rent.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We rented a house with a Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Roytenberg who had-- who was on [BACKROUND NOISE] [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mynutoba ?] Avenue.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His wife had died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was alone, so he shared the house with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was looking for work, he couldn't get work, but he opened a-- a store with-- with a partner.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The partner was a Canadian, a Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Cohen. ?] And they bought a store on Gordon Avenue that was open from 8:00 in the morning to 12:00 midnight.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was the only store in Winnipeg that was open that late, and he start going from the north end to the south end by bus every day, and staying till midnight.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by the time he came home, it was quite late and getting up in the morning again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was good times.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
